pan class="main-menu__collections-caret "></span></a><ul class="main-menu__collections-content main-menu__collections-content--collections
             " style="height:0"><li class="main-menu__collection"><a href="https://events.festival.fastcompany.com/"><h3 class="main-menu__events-link">Innovation Festival</h3></a><a href="https://events.fastcompany.com/fcgrill/"><h3 class="main-menu__events-link">The Grill</h3></a></li></ul></div><a href="https://www.fastcompany.com/magazine/" class="main-menu__current-issue">Current Issue</a><div class="main-menu__subscription"><a href="https://www.fastcompany.com/magazine/" class="main-menu__mag-cover" style="background-image:url(//www.fastcompany.com/magazine/latest-cover.jpg)">Current Issue</a><div class="main-menu__subscription-button-row"><a href="https://magazine.fastcompany.com/loc/FST/sidenav1999" class="main-menu__subscribe-link" title="subscribe">SUBSCRIBE</a></div></div><div class="main-menu__social-menu"><div class="main-menu__social-text"><span class="main-menu__social-text-hed">Follow us:</span></div><div class="main-menu__social-list"><a href="https://www.facebook.com/FastCompany/" class="main-menu__social-button main-menu__social-button--facebook" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="https://images.fastcompany.net/image/upload/v1541690325/fcweb/fb-icon-circle-777777_hs2as9.svg" alt="Social media icons"/></a><a href="https://twitter.com/fastcompany" class="main-menu__social-button main-menu__social-button--twitter" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="https://images.fastcompany.net/image/upload/v1541690328/fcweb/tw-icon-circle-777777_fwaqmc.svg" alt="Social media icons"/></a><a href="https://www.instagram.com/fastcompany/" class="main-menu__social-button main-menu__social-button--instagram" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="https://images.fastcompany.net/image/upload/v1541690325/fcweb/insta-icon-circle-777777_tciktn.svg" alt="Social media icons"/></a><a href="https://getpocket.com/explore/fastcompany.com" class="main-menu__social-button main-menu__social-button--pocket" target="_blank" rel="noopener no